    {
      "id": "PopularPost79839",
      "post_content": "I run this, and you're right it is slow, but it's a great augmentation. Let's say you have two Megrim's in play and you attack with Hypnotic Specter. The opponent has to take it to the face because they don't have flying. The opponent takes 2 to the face from the Specter, and have to toss a card due to its ability. This triggers the two Megrims for 2 damage apiece; for a total of 6 damage.\n  \n   \nReply that same scenario with Larceny on deck as well; now when the Specter attacks it does 2 to the opponent itself, trigger its own ability AND Larceny which results in the opponent having to discard 2 cards; which triggers both Megrim's twice. Larceny ups the damage from 6 to 10, and further locks down the opponent by causing them to loose the second card.\n  \n   \nIt's a great augmentation in a Blue Black deck where you've got enough counters to protect your enchantments.",
      "posted_by": "PhyrexianLobbiest",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost79839\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_post\">I run this, and you're right it is slow, but it's a great augmentation.  Let's say you have two Megrim's in play and you attack with Hypnotic Specter.  The opponent has to take it to the face because they don't have flying.  The opponent takes 2 to the face from the Specter, and have to toss a card due to its ability.  This triggers the two Megrims for 2 damage apiece; for a total of 6 damage.\r<br/> <br/>Reply that same scenario with Larceny on deck as well; now when the Specter attacks it does 2 to the opponent itself, trigger its own ability AND Larceny which results in the opponent having to discard 2 cards; which triggers both Megrim's twice.  Larceny ups the damage from 6 to 10, and further locks down the opponent by causing them to loose the second card.\r<br/> <br/>It's a great augmentation in a Blue Black deck where you've got enough counters to protect your enchantments.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '79839'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy14501\">PhyrexianLobbiest</span>\r\n                                (6/15/2010 11:14:04 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl04_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftClearSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightClearSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>"
